<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Megachile fortis</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1872</font></b><br>
<small><i>Megachile emoryi </i>Cockerell, 1904; <i>Megachile fortis var vestali </i>Cockerell, 1913; <i>Megachile &#40;Xanthosarus&#41; fortis </i>Cresson, 1872</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Megachilidae">Megachilidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Megachile">Megachile</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Phaenosarus&name=Megachile&flags=subgenus:"><i>Phaenosarus</i></a></small>
